{"tid":1214721,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(竉物一問）呀狗強好奇怪","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T05:35:00.000Z","uid":32005,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b62921139f0f00445026b9d6d3e686b4e68a79cb","tid":1214721,"uid":32005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:07:38.000Z","msg":"有隻狗叫狗強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢原本只係有少少傻下傻下 有少少蠢<br />\n咁佢就去左寵物學園想做一隻好狗想保護主人<br />\n但呀狗強一出左學園就變到好奇怪 出街就好亢奮 仲會亂咬主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n.<br />\n我想問下寵物學園係咪會亂幫狗仔打興奮針 好擔心狗強同其他狗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f9f32c8933717550aed0b67eedbf6590fc9772","tid":1214721,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:13:30.000Z","msg":"呼籲各大市民聽日行街見到警犬就噓佢<br />\n屌多兩句老母都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b80f09d92df36bed75ad3f60a565fa058987af","tid":1214721,"uid":32005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:35:00.000Z","msg":"仲會唔會有方法救到狗強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定拎去人道毀滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}